The Boys are back in town! When we last left Billy Butcher and his lot, things were not looking good for the anti-supe squad. This season, there are even more twists and turns as The Seven gets a new member in the social media savvy Stormfront, Billy gets reunited with the love of his life, and we get way more Billy Joel than we predicted. That plus Dawn of the Seven, Brave Maeve Lasagna, and Homelander loving himself as only he could, in our Season 2 breakdown of The Boys on Amazon Prime Video.  **\*If you or a loved one were exposed to Compound V, you may be entitled to financial compensation. Vought has given the drug to multiple victims, without their knowledge or consent.  
  
Please** leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [**ComicBookClique.com**](../episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
